      public Movie(int year, String title, int duration, String genre, String rating, double score, String director, String actor1, String actor2, String actor3)
      This custom constructor takes in 10 parameters and creates a Movie object
      Parameters:
      year - A movie's release year
      title - A movie's title
      duration - A movie's duration, in minutes
      genre - A movie's genre
      rating - A movie's rating
      score - A movie's score
      director - The movie's director
      actor1 - The first actor of a movie
      actor2 - The second actor of a movie
      actor3 - The third actor of a movie
